data.description: Discover endless possibilities on this enchanting property with 12 acres of Bahia grass pasture, perfect for your four-legged friends to roam freely. This charming home offers privacy and flexibility – make it your primary residence or a guest retreat while you plan and build your dream home. Outbuildings are ready for chickens or 4-H projects, and a two-stall barn with a feed/tack room awaits. Surrounding the property are various types of trees including Pecan, crêpe myrtle, Mimosa, cedar, and pine trees, adding to the serene ambiance. Don't miss out on the chance to create your ideal living space in this idyllic setting.
